public financial management inc private company information  bloomberg july    am et capital markets company overview of public financial management inc snapshot people company overview public financial management inc provides financial and investment advisory services it engages in capital planning revenue forecasting and evaluation resource allocation structuring documentation and execution the company also provides strategic and financial consulting investment consulting bond pricing debt management state revolving fund services quantitative strategies and structured products in addition it offers investment management solutions including short term cash separate accounts bond proceeds management local government investment pools managed accounts program and opeb investments and investment services for arbitrage rebate escrow structuring guarant public financial management inc provides financial and investment advisory services it engages in capital planning revenue forecasting and evaluation resource allocation structuring documentation and execution the company also provides strategic and financial consulting investment consulting bond pricing debt management state revolving fund services quantitative strategies and structured products in addition it offers investment management solutions including short term cash separate accounts bond proceeds management local government investment pools managed accounts program and opeb investments and investment services for arbitrage rebate escrow structuring guaranteed investment contracts and swaps the company provides investment advice and portfolio management services for governmental and notforprofit organizations corporations pension funds and other institutions as well as serves education healthcare higher education public power solid waste sportsrecreation state revolving funds transportation and water and wastewater industries the company was founded in  and is based in philadelphia pennsylvania with additional offices in providence rhode island and rest of the united states public financial management inc operates as a subsidiary of the pfm group detailed description two logan squareth  arch streetsuite philadelphia pa united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwpfmcomfinancialadvisory key executives for public financial management inc mr john h bonow chief executive officer and managing director mr steve boyle chief financial officer dr martin paul margolis phd chief investment officer managing director and director age  mr leo joseph karwejna chief compliance officer and managing director mr steven alexander managing director compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup most searched private companies company name geographic region lawyers committee for civil rights under law united states nyc inc united states the advertising council inc united states bertelsmann ag europe rush university united states sponsored financial commentaries sponsored links browse companies a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z              request profile update only a company representative may request an update for the company profile documentation will be required to contact public financial management inc please visit wwwpfmcomfinancialadvisory company data is provided by sp global market intelligence please use this form to report any data iss